gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model

Class ProcedureVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.AbstractVariable
      • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.ProcedureVariable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Variable

    @Entity
public final class ProcedureVariable
extends AbstractVariable

    Similar to a MultiSelectVariable, but the selections are a procedure list. This special case is helpful because there are thousands of procedures.

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.

    • Method Detail

      • getProcedures

        public java.util.List<Procedure> getProcedures()

        Returns the List of all active Procedures. Note that this is not a member collection of the ProcedureVariable, it is just for navigability.

        Warning: this collection is not automatically loaded when the ProcedureVariable is loaded from the Database. It must be set via setProcedures(List) after loading.

        Returns:
        an unmodifiable list
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the procedure list has not been set
